=\"sensetop\"><span class=\"def\" hclass=\"def\" htag=\"span\">to start being more careful in your behaviour, especially by spending less money than before</span></span><ul class=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\" hclass=\"examples\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">Small businesses have had to pull their horns in during the recession.</span></li></ul>                                     <div class=\"parallax-container \" data-iaw=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"parallax-abs\">\n            <div id=\"ad_contentslot_2\" class=\"am-default contentslot parallax-fix\">\n                <script>iaw.cmd.push(function() { iaw.display('ad_contentslot_2'); });</script>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n             </li></ol></span> <span class=\"idm-g\" id=\"lock_idmg_6\" sk=\"lockhorns\"><div class=\"top-container\"><div class=\"top-g\" id=\"lock_topg_3\"><div class=\"webtop\"><span class=\"idm\" id=\"lock_idm_1\" cefr=\"c2\">lock horns (with somebody) (over something)</span> </div></div></div><ol class=\"sense_single\" htag=\"ol\"><li class=\"sense\" fkcefr=\"c2\" hclass=\"sense\" htag=\"li\" id=\"lock_sng_8\"><span class=\"sensetop\" htag=\"span\" hclass=\"sensetop\"><span class=\"def\" htag=\"span\" hclass=\"def\">to get involved in an argument with somebody</span></span><ul class=\"examples\" hclass=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">The company has locked horns with the unions over proposed pay cuts.</span></li></ul><span class=\"topic-g\"><span class=\"prefix\">Topics </span><a class=\"Ref\" href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/topic/opinion-and-argument?level=c2\" title=\"Topic opinion-and-argument\"><span class=\"topic\" href=\"l2:functions:opinion_and_argument?cefr=c2\"><span class=\"topic_name\">Opinion and argument</span><span class=\"topic_cefr\">c2</span></span></a></span>      </li></ol></span> <span class=\"idm-g\" sk=\"onhornsofdilemma\" id=\"horn_idmg_3\"><div class=\"top-container\"><di